Suggested workaround (from [1]):
---------------------------------
As a workaround, you setup the plugin as such:

// 1.8
$plugin = new Sabre\DAV\Browser\Plugin(true, false);

// 1.6, 1.7
$plugin = new Sabre_DAV_Browser_Plugin(true, false);

To disable this feature completely.

